    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yandere x yandere x yandere: one must go.</strong><br><br>Yandere x yandere, a vampire-themed Visual Novel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras_big/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404 width=800 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Summary:</u></strong><br><br>Today is the day when you’re totally, definitely, for sure, going to break up with your... not quite lover. You expect contempt, an argument, or a complete lack of reaction, but what you get is—<br><br>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A murder attempt* and a proposal?!<br><br>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*you might or might not be an unreliable narrator</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras_big/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404 width=800 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>What’s in store:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not safe, not sane, but definitely consensual yandere romance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable yandere protagonist (name, sprite)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two (2) yandere love interests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 60k words, approximately 5-8 hours of playthrough (depending on your reading speed) for 100% completion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Playable Modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story Mode:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main storyline with only the relevant POVs unlocked,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 out of 8 endings available</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration Mode:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 routes (X, Levon, mixed) with 2 branches per route,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple branches of varying lengths,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable achievements,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game guide included in achievements, after completing one ending,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All  POVs unlocked on replay for corresponding scenes,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 CGs and 13 item images</p></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras_big/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404 width=800 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Characters:</u></strong><br><br><strong>MC:</strong><br>A bitten vampire, saved by Levon from a group of monster hunters. Sheltered in the mansion of Levon’s soon-to-be (dead) betrothed, MC developed a label-less relationship with his/her/their savior, which grew strained over the years. Currently working as a monster hunter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levon de Nisau:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras/311b970bb92def334e3fbe30d5a76ded.avif?t=1740691404\" width=202 height=344 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coming from a lowly background, Levon rose to power and fortune by the means of inheritance. Merciless, selfish, and oftentimes harsh, he used to navigate life by adopting a charismatic social butterfly persona. Now, being one of the richest and most affluent men in the country, he no longer bothers with such pretense. <br><br><strong>X:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras/753f0ea3ecd0ff047af5079c83c93324.avif?t=1740691404\" width=226 height=343 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Formerly an orphan MC saved from being killed in the witch trials, now a young man who refuses to seek a better future for himself, stubbornly staying in Levon’s mansion as a servant. Despite that, X is rather cocky and brash, even towards his employer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278350/extras_big/feeece914f5f5f11c4e388935017cb8b.avif?t=1740691404 width=800 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Credits:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engine: [Ren'Py by Tom Rothamel]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Writing: [PDRRook], [Dom]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art Assets, GUI Design: [PDRRook]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coding, GUI Coding: [PDRRook], [Dom]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music and SFX: Nicolas Jeudy of DARK FANTASY STUDIO, Ovani Sound, Joel Steudler</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fonts, Free for Personal and Commercial Use: [Prince Valiant], [CAT Altgotisch], [Atkinson Hyperlegible]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kinetic Text Tags Code: [Wattson]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Splash Stock Videos: [Vecteezy]</p></li></ul>",
